name: AttributesTest
description: Unit tests for the Attributes class, focusing on attribute manipulation and iteration.

test_cases.name: html
test_cases.description: Tests the HTML representation and key handling of Attributes.

test_cases.name: testIteratorRemovable
test_cases.description: Tests the removable iterator functionality of Attributes.

test_cases.name: testIteratorUpdateable
test_cases.description: Tests the updateable iterator functionality of Attributes.

test_cases.name: testIteratorHasNext
test_cases.description: Tests the hasNext functionality of the Attributes iterator.

test_cases.name: testIterator
test_cases.description: Tests the basic iterator functionality of Attributes.

test_cases.name: testIteratorSkipsInternal
test_cases.description: Tests that the iterator skips internal attributes in Attributes.

test_cases.name: iteratorThrows
test_cases.description: Tests that the iterator throws NoSuchElementException when exhausted.

test_cases.name: testListSkipsInternal
test_cases.description: Tests that the list representation skips internal attributes in Attributes.

test_cases.name: htmlSkipsInternals
test_cases.description: Tests that the HTML representation skips internal attributes in Attributes.

test_cases.name: testIteratorEmpty
test_cases.description: Tests the iterator functionality on an empty Attributes object.

test_cases.name: testIteratorRemove
test_cases.description: Tests the remove functionality of the Attributes iterator.

test_cases.name: testIteratorRemoveConcurrentException
test_cases.description: Tests that the iterator throws ConcurrentModificationException when the underlying collection is modified.

test_cases.name: removeCaseSensitive
test_cases.description: Tests the case sensitivity of the remove method in Attributes.

test_cases.name: testSetKeyConsistency
test_cases.description: Tests the consistency of setting keys in Attributes.

test_cases.name: testBoolean
test_cases.description: Tests the boolean attribute handling in Attributes.

test_cases.name: testSizeWhenHasInternal
test_cases.description: Tests the size calculation when Attributes contains internal keys.

test_cases.name: testBooleans
test_cases.description: Tests the handling of boolean attributes in Attributes.

test_cases.name: booleanNullAttributesConsistent
test_cases.description: Tests the consistency of null boolean attributes in Attributes.

test_cases.name: booleanEmptyString
test_cases.description: Tests the handling of empty string boolean attributes in Attributes.

test_cases.name: booleanCaseInsensitive
test_cases.description: Tests the case insensitivity of boolean attributes in Attributes.

test_cases.name: equalsIsOrderInsensitive
test_cases.description: Tests the order insensitivity of the equals method in Attributes.

test_cases.name: cloneAttributes
test_cases.description: Tests the cloning functionality of Attributes.
